<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Lego Collection</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/main.css">
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/navbar',  {page: '/'}) %>
    
    <div class="container mx-auto p-4">
        <div class="hero bg-base-200 rounded-lg p-6">
            <div class="hero-content text-center">
                <div class="max-w-md">
                    <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold">Welcome</h1>
                    <p class="py-6">Unleash your inner builder and embark on a fascinating journey through the colorful realm of Lego.</p>
                    <button class="btn btn-primary"><a href="/lego/sets">GET STARTED NOW</a></button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <br>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3  gap-4">
            <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-xl">
                <figure>
                    <img class="w_full" src="https://cdn.rebrickable.com/media/sets/001-1.jpg" alt="Gears"/>
                </figure>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h2 class="card-title">Gears</h2>
                    <p>This set was released in America (USA/ CAN) by Samsonite in 1965. It was re-released in 1969 as an educational set(322-4). It was never released in Europe.</p>
                    <div class="card-actions justify-end">
                        <a href="/lego/sets/001-1" class="btn btn-primary">View</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-xl">
                <figure>
                    <img class="w_full" src="https://cdn.rebrickable.com/media/sets/0011-2.jpg" alt="Town Mini-Figures"/>
                </figure>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h2 class="card-title">Town Mini-Figures</h2>
                    <p>There are 3 Minifigs in this inventory, with 3 total quantity.</p>
                    <div class="card-actions justify-end">
                        <a href="/lego/sets/0011-2" class="btn btn-primary">View</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-xl">
                <figure>
                  <img class="w_full" src="https://cdn.rebrickable.com/media/sets/0011-3.jpg" alt="Castle 2 for 1 Bonus Offer"/>
                </figure>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h2 class="card-title">Castle 2 for 1 Bonus Offer</h2>
                    <p>There are 2 unique sets in this inventory.</p>
                    <div class="card-actions justify-end">
                        <a href="/lego/sets/0011-3" class="btn btn-primary">View</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>        
    </div>
</body>
</html>